author: Monique Angelica Tiamzon
text:
you're so numb you can't even feel what I feel every time you do something wrong to me for you I'm the one who's always wrong

if you ask me why I can't give you my full trust anymore because of what you're doing to me that hurt me so much

author: Monique Angelica Tiamzon
text:
You always like that and I hate that

You always treated me like you didn't care for me

you always think of yourself you don't think of how I feel

you always raise your pride, you don't pay attention to those around you when you are already hurting someone
